                            <comment id="14219570" author="andrewor14" created="Thu, 20 Nov 2014 16:41:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for filing this Josh. It is actually supported and the docs are just out-dated. I&apos;ll get to fixing them shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14236155" author="andrewor14" created="Fri, 5 Dec 2014 21:39:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This was actually fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/2461&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/2461&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14286466" author="asimjalis" created="Wed, 21 Jan 2015 22:47:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This bug should be reopened. The doc needs some more changes.&lt;br/&gt;
Doc: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/master/docs/submitting-applications.md&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/master/docs/submitting-applications.md&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
